    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the definition of showroom quality, representing a rare find for the most meticulous collector. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional ceramic coating, resulting in a mirror-like shine with absolutely zero stone chips, swirls, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple without a single crease, and the carpets have been protected by original factory mats since day one. Every switch, button, and digital display functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, document-supported service history and a driving experience that is tight, powerful, and remarkably smooth. Garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, this car is indistinguishable from new. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
